OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of late
OL,7,Fsunshine. Overnight remaining dry and
OL,8,Flargely clear although some patchy
OL,9,Fmist and fog developing in places,
OL,10,Fespecially near the moors.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry on
OL,13,FWednesday with plenty of sunshine.
OL,14,FFeeling very warm, although a little
OL,15,Fcooler near coasts as sea breezes
OL,16,Fdevelop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
